generativeToken.name: A Machine can have a Soul

metadata.name: A Machine can have a Soul
metadata.description:
Viewed as an asymmetric version of inkblots, I saw faces, spirits, trees, monsters, horses, and more. I wonder what you will see in the random art you mint?

After generating several variations, I thought, “When I was younger, why weren’t kids taught how to apply math to art? I never knew math could be so creative!!”

50% of all primary sales will be donated to Ukraine's Defence and Demining fund via the @WhitePay_com wallet generated in my previous piece tz1commVTYvqHBjxjiin4oytJVgqW7AQhnMy. Also, 33.4% of all secondary sales royalties will go to the same fund, and 33.3% of all secondary sales royalties will go to the minter in perpetuity.
